<Layout title="About">

<SubSection title="Navigation and usage">
        <p class="mb-5 d-none d-xl-block">
            Use the expandable sidebar menu on the left to explore the topics for a certain course, and navigate to your desired page.
        </p>

        <Searchbar />

        <p class="my-3">
            Use the searchbar that looks exactly like the one above to lookup a particular keyword (I'm in the navbar at the top)! You can filter between the courses, or search across all of them at once.
        </p>
       

    <CalloutContainer slot="cards">
        <CalloutCard>
            You can toggle between light and dark mode? The button is located in the navbar at the top of each page. On desktop, it should be right above me! 
        </CalloutCard>
    </CalloutContainer>
</SubSection>


 
