<SubSection title="Importance of collaboration in learning">
    <p>The TAM 2XX staff has worked on engineering education research with the <a target="_blank" href="https://www.colearnlab.org/" >Collaborative Learning Laboratory</a> in the Department of Education. This project is called Collaborative Support Tools for Engineering Problem Solving (CSTEPS).</p>

    <p>As Teaching and Course Assistants, we try to encourage a collaborative environment using the principle of this  <a target="_blank" href="/about/CollabTeachingSequence.pdf">teaching sequence.</a></p>
</SubSection>
